                    July 1, 2021,  2:23pm
                  </time>
                  <meta itemprop='dateModified' content='2021-07-01T14:23:38Z'>
              <span itemprop='position'>2</span>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>Redash doesn’t have a <code>create_data_source</code> permission. To make a data source a user must simply be an admin. We would certainly review a pull request implementing this enhancement. If this is something you’d like to tackle, please reach out to us first to discuss the implementation as this could relate to our future permissions re-write.</p>
            </div>

